long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Do you have covid news fatigue? Wish that anti-vaxxers could be (humorously) taken down a peg? Vax to Wipe replaces all instances of vaccine information with “ass wipe.” Guaranteed to make your newsreading and doomscrolling life at least 1.2x more humorous than it was before.
